profile.bio: Bought up in the UK, I graduated in Philosophy and Literature at the University of Sussex. I am a writer and musician (guyjames.com), currently living off-grid in a log cabin in the Pyrenees. Also working with Guerrilla Translation, FairCoop and the CIC.
